data.title: Not bad for a pho place
data.text:
Its not Bolsa, but on a cold day, this place can do the trick.  I can't really give it 4 stars as the service isn't the best, but, its clean, the staff is fast, and friendly. It just takes a while to get your check.

Parking can be a bit tricky, as its in a strip mall with other tenants.
